#: ../../N/netdead.rst:5
msgid "netdead"
msgstr "netdead"

#: ../../N/netdead.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../N/netdead.rst:9
msgid ""
"[IRC] The state of someone who signs off :ref:`IRC`\\, perhaps during a "
":ref:`netburp`\\, and doesn't sign back on until later. In the interim, he "
"is \"dead to the net\". Compare :ref:`link-dead`\\."
msgstr ""
"[IRC] おそらく\\ :ref:`netburp`\\ の最中に\\ :ref:`IRC`\\ "
"からサインオフし、後になるまでサインオンし直さない人の状態。その間、彼は「ネットに対して死んでいる」。\\ :ref:`link-dead`\\ "
"と比較せよ。"
